text: Sofia Nilsson (born 12 June 1990) is a Swedish football midfielder who currently plays for Djurgårdens IF. She has played Damallsvenskan football for Stattena IF and Djurgårdens IF. ==References== Category:Swedish women's footballers Category:Djurgårdens IF Fotboll (women) players Category:Damallsvenskan players Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders
